{
  "stem": "17001.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I said to her, the gendarme had taken us already, even before, at home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then I had seen that some of these people who we were together in the same house in the ghetto, that they were-- because in Europe, you had this matchbox that-- it was a small little box, like they had in this country, they have the Matchbox cars, the same thing.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It had matches in them it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they had full of $100 pengo.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were burning it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was they were walking between the people who were seated on the ground.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said, my god.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Here they are burning the money, but they didn't had money to pay for the milk.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So once we were pushed up on the train, 80 person with the bundles, small, big, heavy, light, had to go up into the cattle train.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When we went up to the cattle train, my father made sure that we were seated, you know, back to the train.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they-- before they closed the door, they handed us one bucket.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "One bucket.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we didn't know that time what is the bucket for.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And no longer we were seated there, people had to relieve themself.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had to the-- so they wanted to use the bucket.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So my father said, OK.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I have this blanket.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Two people should hold it around that until they relieve themself into the bucket.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And as the train was going, it wasn't pleasant, because the odor was circulating all over and the people was perspiring.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was hot and everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "As we were going, we were watching-- they were watching through the little slip on the-- on the wagon where we are passing by.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
